description: Chicken and Waffles are an unlikely pair but if you've never had them together, this is a must try! At Oklahoma City's Taste of Soul truck they serve sweet fluffy waffles alongside hot and crispy fried chicken that simply melts in your mouth. If you're looking for the perfect comfort food indulgence, look no further than the Taste of Soul Chicken and Waffle truck!
name: Taste of Soul Chicken and Waffle
